  "detailed_description": "How far can a childhood paper airplane fly.?<br />\r\nWhere you can go depends on you.<br />\r\nControl your paper plane to avoid the black object of the flying case and fly to the finish line. If hit, the star life will disappear, and all star life will disappear as a failure.<br />\r\nWang Ximeng's' Thousand Miles of Rivers and Mountains', Van Gogh's' Starry Sky ', Monet's' Water Lily', you can operate your paper plane to shuttle through scenes like a master's painting, flying towards the destination.",
